{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"],"fields":{"title":{"boost":1000.0},"text":{"boost":1.0},"tags":{"boost":1000000.0}}},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"Patlab","text":"<p>Generate beautiful text-based patterns in Python with a clean API.</p>"},{"location":"#quick-example","title":"\ud83d\ude80 Quick Example","text":"<pre><code>from patlab.pyramid import pyramid\nprint(pyramid(4))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   *\n  ***\n *****\n*******\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"#features","title":"\u2728 Features","text":"<ul> <li>Simple and clean API</li> <li>Multiple pattern types</li> <li>Custom characters</li> <li>Numeric patterns</li> <li>Hollow patterns</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#installation","title":"\ud83d\udce6 Installation","text":"<pre><code>pip install patlab\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"#documentation","title":"\ud83d\udcda Documentation","text":"<ul> <li>Getting Started</li> <li>Pattern Guides</li> <li>Examples</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#why-patlab","title":"\ud83d\udca1 Why Patlab?","text":"<p>Patlab helps beginners and developers:</p> <ul> <li>Learn pattern logic</li> <li>Avoid repetitive code</li> <li>Quickly generate visual patterns</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#links","title":"\ud83d\udd17 Links","text":"<ul> <li>GitHub: https://github.com/sayampradhan/patlab</li> <li>PyPI: https://pypi.org/project/patlab/</li> </ul>"},{"location":"api/","title":"API Reference","text":""},{"location":"api/#square","title":"Square","text":"<p>::: patlab.square</p>"},{"location":"api/#pyramid","title":"Pyramid","text":"<p>::: patlab.pyramid</p>"},{"location":"api/#right-triangle","title":"Right Triangle","text":"<p>::: patlab.right_triangle</p>"},{"location":"getting-started/","title":"Getting Started","text":""},{"location":"getting-started/#installation","title":"Installation","text":"<pre><code>pip install patlab\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"getting-started/#basic-usage","title":"Basic Usage","text":"<pre><code>from patlab.square import square\n\nprint(square(3))\n</code></pre> <p>Output:</p> <pre><code>***\n***\n***\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/","title":"Pyramid","text":""},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#centered-pyramid","title":"Centered Pyramid","text":"<pre><code>from patlab.pyramid import pyramid\nprint(pyramid(4))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   *\n  ***\n *****\n*******\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#left-aligned","title":"Left-Aligned","text":"<pre><code>print(pyramid(4, alignment=\"left\"))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>*\n**\n***\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#right-aligned","title":"Right-Aligned","text":"<pre><code>print(pyramid(4, alignment=\"right\"))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   *\n  **\n ***\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#inverted","title":"Inverted","text":"<pre><code>print(pyramid(4, inversion=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>*******\n *****\n  ***\n   *\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#hollow","title":"Hollow","text":"<pre><code>print(pyramid(4, hollow=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   *\n  * *\n *   *\n*******\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/pyramid/#numeric","title":"Numeric","text":"<pre><code>print(pyramid(4, numeric=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   1\n  121\n 12321\n1234321\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/square/","title":"Square","text":""},{"location":"patterns/square/#basic-usage","title":"Basic Usage","text":"<pre><code>from patlab.square import square\nprint(square(4))\n</code></pre> <p>Output:</p> <pre><code>****\n****\n****\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/square/#custom-character","title":"Custom Character","text":"<pre><code>print(square(4, \"#\"))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>####\n####\n####\n####\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/triangle/","title":"Right Triangle","text":""},{"location":"patterns/triangle/#basic","title":"Basic","text":"<pre><code>from patlab.right_triangle import right_triangle\nprint(right_triangle(4))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>*\n**\n***\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/triangle/#right-aligned","title":"Right-Aligned","text":"<pre><code>print(right_triangle(4, alignment=\"right\"))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>   *\n  **\n ***\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/triangle/#inverted","title":"Inverted","text":"<pre><code>print(right_triangle(4, inversion=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>****\n***\n**\n*\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/triangle/#hollow","title":"Hollow","text":"<pre><code>print(right_triangle(4, hollow=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>*\n**\n* *\n****\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"patterns/triangle/#numeric","title":"Numeric","text":"<pre><code>print(right_triangle(4, numeric=True))\n</code></pre> <pre><code>1\n12\n123\n1234\n</code></pre>"}]}